column724:
DB changes for prefill enrollment (table/sequence SEQ_TU_PREFILL_ENROLLMENT_ID) from 98.6+ were not fully applied in Stage 1: table/sequence DB PRs were not executed there, and the synonym and grant for the sequence were not run, so uii0web could not access the sequence. Backend threw ORA-00942 on select seq_tu_prefill_enrollment_id.nextval from dual, which appeared to users as "This functionality is not available at this time. Please try again later." (RCA: Mayank – logs indicated Mayur’s table/sequence changes were not executed in Stage 1.)
Fix: Synonym and grant were run in Stage 1:
CREATE OR REPLACE PUBLIC SYNONYM SEQ_TU_PREFILL_ENROLLMENT_ID FOR SEQ_TU_PREFILL_ENROLLMENT_ID;
GRANT SELECT ON SEQ_TU_PREFILL_ENROLLMENT_ID TO uii0web;
Sequence is now accessible by uii0web.

