column34:
Create Jenkins jobs for each XML suite:

* {{CAT_Smoke_Login}}
* {{CAT_Smoke_Enrollment}}
* {{CAT_Smoke_Withdrawal}}
* {{CAT_Smoke_Contribution}}
* {{CAT_Smoke_Maintenance}}

Integrate into the CAT deploy pipeline to trigger automatically post-deployment.

*Acceptance Criteria:*

* Jenkins jobs created and visible in pipeline view.
* Jobs trigger post successful CAT deploy.
* Notifications configured for Swapnil & Dev team.

